 John Davidson
(II)


 
Actor |
 
Soundtrack





They don't come any nicer than John Davidson. The dark-haired, Pittsburgh-born singer/TV personality, who was born in 1941 and the son of a Baptist minister, is highly-defined and sometimes cursed by his clean-cut, fresh-faced, apple-cheeked handsomeness. After graduating from high school in White Plains, New York, and earning a B.A. in Theater ...            
See full bio »
            
 


Born:

December 13, 
     
1941

            in
            Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, USA





